{"tid":1739943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2019重出江湖，第九次過大海征戰","createTime":"2019-11-19T19:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T18:01:49.000Z","uid":328223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd83e4ad46d6cc0713b970597dfc67d00ebbba3a","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"大家可能都忘記當年的故事了，不過都是些不太要緊的事<br />\n自第一注起，已三年了，三年間發生了很多事，不管是開心的，傷心的<br />\n目前生活尚算愜意，閒時去下旅行，玩下樂器，有點小確幸的感覺<br />\n本來，我應該安於這種雖平淡但美好的生活，不會再次揮軍征戰<br />\n但是，自6月以來，或親身見證，或圖文影片見證<br />\n香港發生的一切一切，不其然令我想起當初隻身飄洋過海的經歷<br />\n當然，那時我不是做什麼偉大的事，只是純粹的賭博，無法與現今的事相題並論<br />\n即使是現在我將要做的事，也與現今香港的事無甚關係<br />\n只是，不知為何，看到人們燃燒自我，對抗命運的行徑，就好像看到那時的我<br />\n尤其看到「寧為玉碎，不作瓦全」「寧作飛灰，不作浮塵」此等口號<br />\n這不就是我當年的座右銘嗎?<br />\n我反思了自身，這些年來我都在做了些什麼<br />\n我只是在苟且偷安，我不想承認真正的自我<br />\n我，就是一個喜歡快意恩仇的賭徒<br />\n如今我醒悟了，我將遵從心中真正的我而活<br />\n作為一個賭徒而活<br />\n<br />\n我已匯了1900萬現金去金沙，這是我目前可動用的現金<br />\n餘下都是一時三刻難以變現的房產，加起來就是當年金沙贏的8000多萬<br />\n依照慣例，如不幸清袋，會離開塵世，寧為玉碎，不作瓦全<br />\n房產不會動用，如不幸戰敗，就留俾家人當補償<br />\n這次就好似上年年初第八次復出征戰的延續一樣&hellip;只是當時我心中尚存迷惘<br />\n事隔快將兩年，這次我心已如明鏡止水，無比澄明<br />\n是次目標：隨心<br />\n<br />\n一如以往，送首歌俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年我越過重重險境，發生了一次又一次奇蹟<br />\n希望這次香港都可以<br />\n<br />\nARCH ENEMY - War Eternal<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InRMwptcgAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DInRMwptcgAo&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=92b8be97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InRMwptcgAo</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我一直不想開連登ACC，但由於最近香港的事，我終於開左...<br />\n呢次我高登連登兩邊都開POST紀錄，但高登開先，始終上了高登十鳩幾年...這是我的根..."},{"pid":"a97cdcf4472340fa0a10d8501db1d21a2e31a26b","tid":1739943,"uid":49211,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:45:55.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死賭仔"},{"pid":"b9fc1e3484442e5493642f77c599c4670fc16b98","tid":1739943,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"8000萬都唔滿足&hellip;<br />\n究竟你咩構造？<br />\n<br />\n利申：有係高登追過你live，記得你用過500萬買匯豐"},{"pid":"5fa30bc97f672c98253e374950a2076ae34fa2d4","tid":1739943,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:45:40.000Z","msg":"真係高登1349？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賭命大師"},{"pid":"65d8cb1db83f6f72843079b99dff8347aea6686b","tid":1739943,"uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:18:27.000Z","msg":"有兩千萬閒錢有無諗過攞少少幫吓抗爭者"},{"pid":"ba089e228b3be15948155dfbf9c266f873da2aaa","tid":1739943,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65d8cb1db83f6f72843079b99dff8347aea6686b","tid":1739943,"uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:18:27.000Z","msg":"有兩千萬閒錢有無諗過攞少少幫吓抗爭者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:24:29.000Z","msg":"呢句真"},{"pid":"1d13629196f59d7a2414d87d4c6ea385306f71df","tid":1739943,"uid":127320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:08:43.000Z","msg":"邊到可以重溫你既威水史？"},{"pid":"9470663d5835f4c427aa0be4e7d23637e598ae5f","tid":1739943,"uid":184590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5cc2c65b8a271aad46c10f3ab02db080bbff1249","tid":1739943,"uid":120906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:57:38.000Z","msg":"玩咩玩到8千萬？ 8+6？"},{"pid":"a415ef3f38cf2137819d9fb9237cdd5de9b26ffe","tid":1739943,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 咪撚亂鳩話自己寧為玉碎 不為瓦全啦<br />\n賭仔講到自己咁偉大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4485266b14540adcffb2480aed155766158a8fff","tid":1739943,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65d8cb1db83f6f72843079b99dff8347aea6686b","tid":1739943,"uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:18:27.000Z","msg":"有兩千萬閒錢有無諗過攞少少幫吓抗爭者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"c0b1e64fc909167820b083bf0a516786f5fbcfe7","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"20號過左去金沙城中心, 贏100萬...住左一晚跟住閃人<br />\n我以為心已如明鏡止水, 但1900萬籌碼上到台後, 卻依然心存迷惘<br />\n縱使係咁, 上天都冇離棄我...久別再臨時依然給予我肯定<br />\n1900萬上台, 塊塊50萬碼<br />\n第一鋪買50萬閒, 9點勝<br />\n第二鋪買50萬莊, 6點勝一半<br />\n第三鋪買25萬閒, 8贏7<br />\n第四鋪飛, 公+A VS A+10和<br />\n2000萬離台, 淨勝100萬, 時長約40分鐘<br />\n拎左一晚房, 公關俾左間CONRAD頂樓總統套房我, 其實D分唔夠用來住, 可能見我N年冇來...<br />\n訓完一晚, 第二日2000萬上台<br />\n諗左好耐, 但心中依然好亂, 好猶豫, 結果一鋪都冇買, 將D錢全數匯返香港<br />\n係賭台上猶豫乃係大忌, 所以都係暫時收兵, 我修為依然到家...<br />\n<br />\nWinning proof, 成日話冇證明, 有證明又話賭場打手點整都得, 不過都照PO...<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100333193_802f37105b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100333193_802f37105b_b.jpg&h=facef463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻房第一次住, 一廳兩房, 都幾靚, 照舊大鄉里出城又影相又拍片<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qW67ew5Vdq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqW67ew5Vdq0&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=cbfaec6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qW67ew5Vdq0</a><br />\n<br />\n廳<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100840241_7d05acf4de_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100840241_7d05acf4de_b.jpg&h=760a0b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49101038007_361f15eed7_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49101038007_361f15eed7_b.jpg&h=fef80de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100333793_e204939353_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100333793_e204939353_b.jpg&h=e59cc9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49101037712_3c9d6a37be_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49101037712_3c9d6a37be_b.jpg&h=69e6a194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙床房<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100839646_b6af38d2f2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100839646_b6af38d2f2_b.jpg&h=9d3a4e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大床房<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100839561_72a4a3cd45_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100839561_72a4a3cd45_b.jpg&h=8de5b07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n房型牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100839501_84326c4b19_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100839501_84326c4b19_b.jpg&h=bd713dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n窗外景觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49100333268_df61715119_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49100333268_df61715119_b.jpg&h=b4ab18fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"104d13affb655cb4a47192cea66500a97c4edcdf","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"21號係個特別的日子, 縱使身在澳門, 凌晨先返到, 但我依然心繫香港<br />\n記得721當日, 我都係元朗站&hellip;<br />\n果日果個時間差D坐左地鐵, 最後坐左巴士, 去到途中先知元朗站附近出事<br />\n去到時鄉黑剛散水, 得返姍姍來遲的POPO<br />\n睇直播既應該會見到之後冇幾耐月台D人落返來<br />\n全場屌柒POPO, 差D開片, 最尾POPO退走開唔成, 我諗佢地都怕左果種氣勢<br />\n呢段我記得特別清楚, 因為現場親身感受果種群情洶湧既氣勢真係好強<br />\n就好似所有人合而為一咁, 人雖然唔多, 但我覺得甚至比百萬人出來時更強<br />\n果陣我諗起1984裡面果句<br />\n「他們不到覺悟的時候，就永遠不會造反；他們不造反，就不會覺悟。」<br />\n跟住POPO走哂, 見又冇乜野, 我都閃人, 但返到去先知鄉黑又返轉頭&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手執千萬現金, 加數千萬房產, 唔算多, 但都唔少<br />\n諗過移民, 但自從呢日, 同埋之後種種既事, 我決定留低<br />\n我曾經認為唔會有人再出來, 所以都諗定閃人<br />\n但見到大家果份勇氣, 我改變了<br />\n我不是勇武, 但必要時都會盡一分力<br />\n集合眾人力量, 錢其實唔缺, 只係形勢真係唔太有利, 潑冷水都係咁話...<br />\n香港個勢真係只能見步行步"},{"pid":"23f404c1c6b0ffaff6c3a90e14f156f1ffa3c243","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:50:18.000Z","msg":"送多首歌俾大家<br />\n蔡國權 - 天意人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjaeaRmc61w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEjaeaRmc61w&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=a00fc6c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjaeaRmc61w</a><br />\n<br />\n朦朧的東方 遠古開始的一套<br />\n萬物生於天意的國度 凡人的一生<br />\n幾多得到得不到 盡在天公手裡操<br />\n但若天可知 世間種種的苦惱<br />\n為什麼不稍作點引導 為什麼蒼生<br />\n想得的偏得不到 許多基本的美好<br />\n莫說癡與夢 天不許我行半步<br />\n用我哀與怒 也要奮力試比高<br />\n人間怎麼猜得到 天意的喜與怒<br />\n千秋興衰如何定去路 人生總可知得到<br />\n溫暖給它記號 風波中 覓前路<br />\n莫問知不知 天公衰老不衰老<br />\n只知此生依我心去做 莫問可不可<br />\n最終得到得不到 亦莫須天公讚好<br />\n自問心比天更高"},{"pid":"14a4664d96b73122b703b264acb8cbe6c207d88f","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9fc1e3484442e5493642f77c599c4670fc16b98","tid":1739943,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"8000萬都唔滿足&hellip;<br />\n究竟你咩構造？<br />\n<br />\n利申：有係高登追過你live，記得你用過500萬買匯豐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"500萬買匯豐真係好耐, 果陣岩岩開始<br />\n咁你都記得, 我都差D忘記左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ec96daa317f97c1f7810ccc4ecfcde68a1116a","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa30bc97f672c98253e374950a2076ae34fa2d4","tid":1739943,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:45:40.000Z","msg":"真係高登1349？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賭命大師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"真, 高登都開左同樣POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6058b2b33458881ef99179a37f354b152d2af02c","tid":1739943,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20ec96daa317f97c1f7810ccc4ecfcde68a1116a","tid":1739943,"uid":328223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa30bc97f672c98253e374950a2076ae34fa2d4","tid":1739943,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:45:40.000Z","msg":"真係高登1349？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賭命大師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"真, 高登都開左同樣POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"當時好多人都話你賭場打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />追Live追到好似自己有份賭咁"}]}